=======
LEGEND
=======

. = Background
# = Wall
P = StrongPlayer
* = Rock
_ = Pit
Gun = GunUSingle or GunDSingle or GunRSingle or GunLSingle
Arrow = ArrowU or ArrowD or ArrowL or ArrowR

